# Hay - Premium AI Chat

## Getting Started

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) with your browser to see the result.

## Environment Setup

Create a `.env.local` file:

```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key
MONGODB_URI=your_mongodb_uri
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret
```

## Deploy on Vercel

The easiest way to deploy your Next.js app is to use the [Vercel Platform](https://vercel.com?utm_medium=default-template&utm_source=create-next-app&utm_campaign=create-next-app-readme).
